Dependencies
------------------------------
- OpenCL
- ITK (for image and raw file loading)

Compile
------------------------------
- Use cmake on CMakeList.txt

Usage
------------------------------
For 2D images:
./host filename.jpg size_x size_y mu #iterations [set 1 to use 16 bit floats]

For 3D images:
./host filename.raw size_x size_y size_z mu #iterations [set 1 to use 16 bit floats]
